QuestData.Title: Dredging up a Name
QuestData.Description: Oi, why aren't you addressing me by my proper name? Wait, I don't remember my name, proper or other. Does this mean I have amnesias? Oh no, I don't have a name, please, help!
QuestData.LogDescription: Talk with your assistant and decide on a name for them.

Objectives.Objective: Pick a name for your dredger assistant
